news.title: UK'S Persimmon sees 2024 profit at top end of market view
news.para: Shares in the FTSE 100 builder rose about 4.5% to 1,104 pence in early trade, lifting the broader housing index , with most of its blue-chip peers gaining around 3%.

news.title: Kolkata: Illegal four-storey building keels over during corrective work
news.para: Civic officials said Subho Apartment, tilting at a 45-degree angle, would have to be demolished to prevent a catastrophe. KMC began demolition around 6pm.​

news.title: Varanasi development body begins e-auction of plots under Transport Nagar scheme
news.para: In its official press release on Tuesday, VDA stated that the auction process will continue until Feb 6.
